<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Ramcharit Manas Chandas on Blowfish</title><link>https://localhost:1313/tags/ramcharit-manas-chandas/</link><description>Recent content in Ramcharit Manas Chandas on Blowfish</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</managingEditor><webMaster>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Mon, 11 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://localhost:1313/tags/ramcharit-manas-chandas/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Sundarkand Dhyanam - सुन्दरकांड ध्यान श्लोकं</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/sundarkand-dhyanam/</link><pubDate>Mon, 11 Jan 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/sundarkand-dhyanam/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/Hanumanji.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="सनदरकड-धयन-शलक">सुन्दरकांड ध्यान श्लोकं&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%a6%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%a1-%e0%a4%a7%e0%a4%af%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b2%e0%a4%95" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="sundarkand-dhyanam">Sundarkand Dhyanam&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#sundarkand-dhyanam" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/008-SundarKandDhyan.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>शान्तं शाश्वतमप्रमेयमनघं निर्वाणशान्तिप्रदं &lt;br>
ब्रह्माशम्भुफणीन्द्रसेव्यमनिशं वेदान्तवेद्यं विभुम्‌। &lt;br>
रामाख्यं जगदीश्वरं सुरगुरुं मायामनुष्यं हरिं &lt;br>
वन्देऽहं करुणाकरं रघुवरं भूपालचूडामणिम्‌॥1॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Jai Sagun Nirgun Roop - जय सगुन निर्गुन रूप</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-sagun-nirgun-roop/</link><pubDate>Wed, 27 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-sagun-nirgun-roop/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="जय-सगन-नरगन-रप">जय सगुन निर्गुन रूप&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%af-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%aa" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="jai-sagun-nirgun-roop">Jai Sagun Nirgun Roop&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#jai-sagun-nirgun-roop" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/070-JaiSagunNirgun.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>Kakbushandi (Crow Sage) says to Bainteya (King of birds) that at the time of Coronation of Rama in Ayodhya Vedas came in the form of birds and recited as following. Please make a note that this is Bhava of Tulasidas Ji in Ramcharitmanas which he has expressed from Balmiki Ramayana and his own sadhana.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Jai Raama Sada Sada Sukhdham Hare - जय राम सदा सुखधाम</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-raama-sada-sada-sukhdham-hare/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-raama-sada-sada-sukhdham-hare/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="जय-रम-सद-सखधम">जय राम सदा सुखधाम&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%af-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a6-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%96%e0%a4%a7%e0%a4%ae" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="jai-raama-sada-sada-sukhdham-hare">Jai Raama Sada Sada Sukhdham Hare&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#jai-raama-sada-sada-sukhdham-hare" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/069-JaiRamSadaSukhdhaam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>When Ravana is killed by Raama then this prayer is done to Raama by Brahma. Keep in mind this is a poetic narration of “Sant Tulasidas Ji” from “Ramcharit Manas” and not an original poem from “Balmiki Ramayan”&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Jai Raama Sobha Dham - जय राम सोभा धाम</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-raama-sobha-dham/</link><pubDate>Sun, 17 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-raama-sobha-dham/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/067-JairamSobhaDham.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;h1 id="जय-रम-सभ-धम">जय राम सोभा धाम&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%af-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%ad-%e0%a4%a7%e0%a4%ae" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="jai-raama-sobha-dham">Jai Raama Sobha Dham&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#jai-raama-sobha-dham" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>When Ravana is killed by Raama then this prayer is done to Raama by Devtas led by Indra. Keep in mind this is a poetic narration of “Sant Tulasidas Ji” from “Ramcharit Manas” and not original poem from “Balmiki Ramayan”&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Jai Jai Surnayak - जय जय सुरनायक</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-jai-surnayak/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-jai-surnayak/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="जय-जय-सरनयक">जय जय सुरनायक&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%af-%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%af-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%af%e0%a4%95" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="jai-jai-surnayak">Jai Jai Surnayak&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#jai-jai-surnayak" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>(तुलसीकृत रामचरित मानस)&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/029-JaijaiSurNayak.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>जय जय सुरनायक जन सुखदायक प्रनतपाल भगवंता। &lt;br>
गो द्विज हितकारी जय असुरारी सिधुंसुता प्रिय कंता।।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Jai Raam Rama Ramanam Samanam - जय राम रमा रमनं समनं</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-raam-rama-ramanam-samanam/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/jai-raam-rama-ramanam-samanam/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="जय-रम-रम-रमन-समन">जय राम रमा रमनं समनं&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%9c%e0%a4%af-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%a8-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%a8" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="jai-raam-rama-ramanam-samanam">Jai Raam Rama Ramanam Samanam&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#jai-raam-rama-ramanam-samanam" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>तुलसीकृत रामचरित मानस&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/031-JaiRaamRamaRamanamSamanam.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>जय राम रमा रमनं समनं । भव ताप भयाकुल पाहि जनम ॥ &lt;br>
अवधेस सुरेस रमेस बिभो । सरनागत मागत पाहि प्रभो ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Parsat Pad Paavan - परसत पद पावन</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/parsat-pad-paavan/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/parsat-pad-paavan/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="परसत-पद-पवन">परसत पद पावन&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4-%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%a6-%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%a8" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="parsat-pad-paavan">Parsat Pad Paavan&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#parsat-pad-paavan" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>तुलसीकृत रामचरित मानस&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/009-parsatPadPaavan.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>परसत पद पावन सोक नसावन प्रगट भई तपपुंज सही। &lt;br>
देखत रघुनायक जन सुख दायक सनमुख होइ कर जोरि रही।।1।।&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Ramchandra Stavan - रामचन्द्र स्तवन</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/ramchandra-stavan/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/ramchandra-stavan/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="रमचनदर-सतवन">रामचन्द्र स्तवन&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae%e0%a4%9a%e0%a4%a8%e0%a4%a6%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%b5%e0%a4%a8" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="ramchandra-stavan">Ramchandra Stavan&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#ramchandra-stavan" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/026-RamchandraStavan.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>श्रीरामचंद्र कृपालु भजमन हरण भाव भय दारुणम् । &lt;br>
नवकंज लोचन, कंज मुख, कर कंज, पद कन्जारुणम ॥1॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Ramchandra Stuti - श्री राम स्तुति:</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/ramchandra-stuti/</link><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/ramchandra-stuti/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/RamcharaitMaanas.jpg" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="शर-रम-सतत">श्री राम स्तुति:&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%b6%e0%a4%b0-%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%ae-%e0%a4%b8%e0%a4%a4%e0%a4%a4" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="ramchandra-stuti">Ramchandra Stuti&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#ramchandra-stuti" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/027-RamchandraStuti.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;p>नमामि भक्त वत्सलं । कृपालु शील कोमलं ॥ &lt;br>
भजामि ते पदांबुजं । अकामिनां स्वधामदं ॥&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Bhaye Pragat Kripala - भए प्रगट कृपाला</title><link>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/bhaye-pragat-kripala/</link><pubDate>Sun, 12 Apr 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>nuno@n9o.xyz (Blowfish)</author><guid>https://localhost:1313/samskrutyatra/bhaye-pragat-kripala/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://localhost:1313/assets/images/samskrut/dRamcharaitMaanas.png" alt="">&lt;/p>
&lt;audio controls>
 &lt;source src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/dasarpai/DAI-mp3/main/dasarpai-mp3/002-BhayaPragatKrupala.mp3" type="audio/mp3">
 Your browser does not support the audio element.
&lt;/audio> 
&lt;h1 id="भए-परगट-कपल">भए प्रगट कृपाला&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#%e0%a4%ad%e0%a4%8f-%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%b0%e0%a4%97%e0%a4%9f-%e0%a4%95%e0%a4%aa%e0%a4%b2" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h1>
&lt;h2 id="bhaye-pragat-kripala">Bhaye Pragat Kripala&lt;a class="td-heading-self-link" href="#bhaye-pragat-kripala" aria-label="Heading self-link">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>When Bhagawan Vishnu incarnate as Raam from Maharani Kaushaliya then this is the conversation between Vishnu and Kaushliya. Keep in mind this is a poetic narration of “Sant Tulasidas Ji” from “Ramcharit Manas” and not original poem from “Balmiki Ramayan”&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>